WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.439 --> 00:00:02.634
The process for expendable supplies

2
00:00:02.634 --> 00:00:06.889
begins with the Clinical Product Review Committee, or CPRC.

3
00:00:06.889 --> 00:00:09.460
This team has the responsibility to approve

4
00:00:09.460 --> 00:00:13.315
expendable item requests and consists of stakeholders

5
00:00:13.315 --> 00:00:16.449
that are charged with ensuring that facility requirements

6
00:00:16.449 --> 00:00:18.694
are valid and approved as needed.

7
00:00:18.694 --> 00:00:23.437
Requests that are above $3,500 go to network contracting.

8
00:00:23.437 --> 00:00:27.477
Those that are at or under $3,500 go to the logistics

9
00:00:27.477 --> 00:00:31.159
inventory manager and a purchase card is used.

10
00:00:31.159 --> 00:00:33.822
Select each checklist item to step through

11
00:00:33.822 --> 00:00:37.303
this process as it applies to expendable supplies.

